column8: All StatsCan geographic locations not mentioned in iCarol. Some names are simliar, but not exact, so the exact values were kept for reference (for example, there is a Kitikmeot region in Nunavut but Stats Can mentioned a "Kitikmeot, Unorganized" region in BC which was not mentioned in iCarol). The format of this data does not align with iCarol formatting, so not every city has a linked region; therefore, the unknown data is marked with "UNKNOWN" for easier viewing in the Pivot Table

Some iCarol records are located outside of Canada, and these are the regions/countries that these records are located in. Not all these records can be found through searching the resource number, but are still on the iCarol export.
